{"tid":2024344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨派正能量] 想香港獨立/自治，但係點解要貶低香港人？","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T12:08:35.000Z","uid":154486,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3d37dcef73977a048276a0e1d31f16823934e586","tid":2024344,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1mQepA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1mQepA.jpg&h=cc0afcca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好多時候將獨立放成「做支那人」既對立面，係因為支那先要獨立<br />\n<br />\n但係大家有冇諗過<br />\n香港人本身有乜野值得獨立？<br />\n<br />\n我係連登同埋網絡上永遠見到都係對於香港人既負面睇法<br />\n<br />\n香港人要番工<br />\n香港人好善忘<br />\n香港人同支那人冇分別<br />\n香港人冇禮貌<br />\n香港人斤斤計較<br />\n香港人怕事<br />\n香港人私仇互屌<br />\n<br />\n冇錯以上全部都係香港人既缺點，香港人同世界所有人一樣，都係唔完美<br />\n<br />\n但係如果一個地方想要獨立<br />\n其實最重要唔係睇有冇軍隊，有冇臨時議會，有冇臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n而係睇香港人<strong>有乜野值得自成一家，值得唔再做人附庸，出黎獨立</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果真係想要獨立<br />\n請大家真係比D信心香港人<br />\n唔只係信手足，<strong>係要信香港人係重要時刻都會做出正確既選擇</strong><br />\n一個民族既誕生，係好依靠互相既信任<br />\n確信自己民族既智慧，大家係歷史洪流之中摸索中前行<br />\n呢一樣先係最緊要<br />\n<br />\n平時呻下香港人有幾on9﹐當然可以<br />\n但係如果你覺得香港人呢個民族有獨立既可能，無論你當下有幾嬲，有幾無力，有幾灰心，請你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>都要相信香港人集體作出既選擇，唔可以放棄<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n記住，他朝香港獨立/自治左，只會係一切既開始。<br />\n<br />\n比個練習大家：<br />\n每一日上連登果陣<br />\n諗多D香港人有乜野好野<br />\n<br />\n我講先：<br />\n我覺得香港文化轉數快過日本，著重歐美既個人主義既同時又尊重集體利益<br />\n<br />\n如果係世界上揾一個係東西文化上完美合壁既地方，我諗真係非香港莫屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要比信心自己，同埋比信心香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447d3f88f608d4a2ba76b2da6ef1d7aa11e9a17b","tid":2024344,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c1b32bcd856c811da4ee2b72c57a10c5b62e7","tid":2024344,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想問想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f7bf00efecc9ca6fa6e4bca63ad35d6f54d3726","tid":2024344,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2617e2ffd99b41d753abc861abeb957d06440cb","tid":2024344,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"我地抗爭要成功 首要改變返我地套mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9021096237a90bb11a459ce5606d2d9e150dd8fc","tid":2024344,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n革命行為本身就係不理性<br />\n如果唔去無條件相信香港人既智慧<br />\n點樣相信獨立後既香港大家都會有好日子過？？"},{"pid":"9a2f9cfb8d8f90d556b47c4b9ed5c3963dddbcff","tid":2024344,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信香港<br />\n相信香港人<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"833df65c0c7d1e1d891aa7fa259488e1484da4a4","tid":2024344,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p